001package edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.util.LinkedList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008public class MeetingListResponse {
009
010  @Expose
011  @SerializedName("next_page_token")
012  private final String nextPageToken = null;
013  @Expose
014  @SerializedName("page_count")
015  private final int pageCount = 0;
016  @Expose
017  @SerializedName("page_number")
018  private final int pageNumber = 0;
019  @Expose
020  private final List<Meeting> meetings = new LinkedList<>();
021
022  public String getNextPageToken() {
023    return nextPageToken;
024  }
025
026  public int getPageCount() {
027    return pageCount;
028  }
029
030  public int getPageNumber() {
031    return pageNumber;
032  }
033
034  public List<Meeting> getMeetings() {
035    return meetings;
036  }
037}
